headline: How To Earn $500 A Month From Goldman Sachs Stock Ahead Of Q4 Earnings
summary: Goldman Sachs Group, Inc (NYSE:GS) will release earnings for its fourth quarter, before the opening bell on Wednesday, Jan. 15. Analysts expect the New York-based investment bank to report quarterly earnings at $8.35 per share. That’s up from $5.48 per share in the year-ago period. Goldman Sachs expects quarterly revenue of $12.42 billion, compared to $11.32 billion a year earlier, according to Benzinga Pro. On Monday, Barclays analyst Jason Goldberg maintained Goldman Sachs with an Overweight.
